Class Transaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractUniqueId
      • Transaction

  • public class Transaction
extends AbstractUniqueId
    The Transaction class is a plain old data structure that contains all the information on a given transaction.

      • updateWith

        public void updateWith(Transaction other)
        Updates this transaction with the information form the specified transaction. This does not change the id of this transaction. It is assumed we are updating with a newer version of the same transaction.
        Parameters:
        other - account to update from
